        Your keys to the<br/>
        <span className="italic" style={{ color: "var(--bio-hi)" }}>A'Space Core</span><br/>
        are ready.
      </h1>
      <p className="serif italic" style={{
        fontSize: 18, color: "var(--amber)",
        opacity: 0.9, margin: "0 0 36px", lineHeight: 1.4,
      }}>
        The universe is bigger on the inside.
      </p>

      {/* Blurred wheel preview */}
      <div style={{
        position: "relative",
        display: "flex", justifyContent: "center", alignItems: "center",
        margin: "0 -24px 40px",
        padding: "24px 0",
