        <div className="mono-xs" style={{ color: "var(--amber)", marginBottom: 10 }}>REDIRECT · MAIN TERMINAL</div>
        <p className="serif italic" style={{ color: "var(--fg-dim)", fontSize: 14, margin: "0 0 14px", lineHeight: 1.45 }}>
          Already at a desk? Return to the main terminal for full onboarding.
